nodes.text: Kevin Layne is a British actor who portrays Finch Dallow (credited as "Resistance Bomber Pilot #1") in the 2017 film Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi. He is also notable for playing a submarine pilot in Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom and a freedom fighter in the 2019 French-Belgium war film L'intervention.
